FT  25 JUN 94 / UK Company News: Wagon acquires Evercheck pref
Wagon Industrial Holdings has acquired the preference share capital of
Evercheck, holding company of Montan Group, from the Royal Bank of Scotland
for Pounds 2.5m. The consideration will be 534,188 shares which have been
conditionally placed.
Wagon acquired Evercheck's ordinary share capital on March 31 for a nominal
consideration.
